Show HN: Storytime AI – Generate custom stories for your kids
text: For months, my wife and I were manually and haphazardly using ChatGPT to generate bedtime stories for our 3-year-old (mostly using her ideas as prompts), so I built this app on top of the ChatGPT API to make bedtime a lot easier.
